,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:23:07.000Z","msg":"乜都炒<br />\n你老母都限量啦<br />\n唔拎埋去炒?"},{"pid":"8ba0dfc80b53af44281aaf181cdbaa64fe7f753f","tid":457550,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜都炒<br />\n你老母都限量啦<br />\n唔拎埋去炒?</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁啦，唔見左萬幾蚊我已經好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a2fa9606779456f25d9075d68841128e8edfbb","tid":457550,"uid":170037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}